Combine SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, KOOL-AID(R) Soft Drink Mix, and 1 cup of the seltzer in a pitcher, stirring until SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener dissolves. Stir in remaining seltzer. Pour 1 cup of the mixture into each of 4 tall glasses; top each serving with 1/2 cup of the frozen yogurt. Serve immediately.